description:
Tonya and Eric, two sustaining members of The Current, share how member support makes The Current thrive.

It’s thanks to members like Tonya and Eric that The Current has been able to rock for the past 20 years. Support The Current today by donating $20 for our 20th anniversary to help us rock for 20 more years! 

Give today at thecurrent.org/donate and find more at thecurrent.org/anniversary

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see previously unreleased recordings from artists such as Brandi Carlile, Tori Amos, Drive-By Truckers, First Aid Kit, Dan Wilson, Atmosphere, Sharon Van Etten, Alt-J, Elle King, Big Thief, Khruangbin, and many more, mixed with recent recordings from artists including Killer Mike, Marcus Mumford, Alex G, Gigi Perez, Sierra Ferrell, Laufey, Gregory Alan Isakov, and others. Check it out now. 

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
